<h2 id="description">Description</h2>

<p><strong>SONUS</strong> app is a speech recognition &amp; synthesis tool.
It uses Google Services (STT and TTS).</p>

<p>The project was created during Makeathon 2021 (TOM Kazakhstan) as a volunteer project to help people with speech and hearing disabilities better interact with the environment.</p>

<h2 id="agreements">Agreements</h2>
<p>Using SONUS app you do accept:</p>

<p><a href="./privacy_policy.html">Privacy Policy</a></p>

